Class Song

  • java.lang.Object
    • Song

  • public class Song
extends java.lang.Object
    This program is part of my response to Project 3 for the class 605.201.81 Intro to Programming Using Java at the JHU EPP CS program. This class is used to create a Song object that has title, item code, etc attributes and appropriate get/set methods for each.
